<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include('../partials/new-head', { title: 'Kidamame Discovery | The Calm App for Kids' ,
  url: 'https://www.kidamame.com/discovery/' }) %>

  <body>
    <%- include('../partials/new-nav', { alwaysScrolled: true, hideNavItems: false, isInnerPage: true }) %>

      <main style="background: var(--white);">
        <!-- PRODUCT -->
        <section class="product" id="apps" style="padding-top: 8rem;">
          <div class="container">
            <p class="section-label reveal"><i class="fa-solid fa-mobile-screen"></i> &nbsp;Our App</p>
            <h2 class="section-title reveal">Kidamame <em>Discovery</em></h2>

            <div class="product-simple-content reveal">
              <p>
                Welcome to a calm, interactive world designed for families. <strong>Kidamame Discovery</strong> replaces
                fast-paced goals and instructions with <strong>child-led exploration</strong>, inviting kids to touch,
                play, and learn at their own pace.
              </p>

              <div class="simple-gallery">
                <img src="/images/gallery/thumbs/kidamame_discovery_home.webp" class="landscape"
                  alt="A wildlife educational app screenshot in the Alps." loading="lazy" />
              </div>

              <h3
                style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.8rem; margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--ink);">
                Pure Exploration & Wonder</h3>
              <p>
                Built entirely around curiosity and <strong>Montessori principles</strong>, there are absolutely
                <strong>no things to win and no puzzles to
                  solve</strong>. Kids simply pan across the landscape, explore the environment, and listen to the
                authentic <strong>sounds of animals and nature</strong>. Tapping the magnifying glass reveals
                beautifully illustrated cards filled with fascinating facts about each element.
              </p>

              <div class="simple-gallery" style="margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">
                <img src="/images/gallery/thumbs/artic_card.webp"
                  alt="A wildlife educational app screenshot in the Artic featuring a polar bear with its cub"
                  loading="lazy" />
                <img src="/images/gallery/thumbs/sonoran.webp"
                  alt="A wildlife educational app screenshot in the African Savannah with mount Kilimanjaro"
                  loading="lazy" />
              </div>

              <h3
                style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.8rem; margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--ink);">
                Interactive Animals, Plants & Natural Phenomena</h3>
              <p>
                The app features <strong>6 stunning scenes</strong>: the Alps, the African Savannah, the
                Australian Outback, the Arctic, the Sonoran Desert, and the Amazon Rainforest. Each sensory-rich biome
                contains <strong>20 or more interactive elements</strong> (animals, plants, and natural phenomena). We
                focus on the "small wonders," showing how even the tiniest creatures hide big secrets. Tap the ostrich
                to see its eggs fall, touch the volcano to trigger a spectacular eruption, or watch the glacier front
                collapse into the sea! With over 120 interactive elements in total, there are <strong>about 400
                  fascinating facts</strong> waiting to be discovered!
              </p>

              <div class="simple-gallery" style="margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">
                <img src="/images/gallery/thumbs/13.webp"
                  alt="A wildlife educational app screenshot in the Australian Red Center with Uluru and a kangaroo"
                  loading="lazy" />
                <img src="/images/gallery/thumbs/11.webp"
                  alt="A wildlife educational app screenshot in the Amazon forest featuring a tucan and a macaw parrot"
                  loading="lazy" />
              </div>

              <h3
                style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.8rem; margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--ink);">
                Quality Time Together</h3>
              <p>
                We designed Kidamame Discovery as a <strong>shared experience</strong>. The app shines when a child
                plays alongside an adult, exploring the biomes together while the parent helps reading the fun facts
                which, by the way, are
                genuinely interesting for adults too! In line with the latest <strong>American Academy of Pediatrics
                  (AAP) recommendations</strong> on screen time, Kidamame is built to encourage co-viewing and
                meaningful family interactions. Our ultimate aspiration is that this shared digital wonder will
                inspire your family to step outside and discover the magic of the real world.
              </p>

              <div class="simple-gallery" style="margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">
                <img src="/images/gallery/thumbs/05.webp"
                  alt="A parent and child exploring nature together with Kidamame Discovery app" loading="lazy" />
                <img src="/images/gallery/thumbs/amazon_forest.webp"
                  alt="A parent and child exploring nature together with Kidamame Discovery app" loading="lazy" />
              </div>

              <div class="promise-block reveal"
                style="background: var(--amber-soft); padding: 3rem; border-radius: 20px; border: 1px solid rgba(245, 165, 42, 0.2); margin-top: 4rem; margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">
                <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                  <div
                    style="width: 50px; height: 50px; flex-shrink: 0; border-radius: 12px; background: var(--amber); color: white; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 1.4rem;">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved"></i>
                  </div>
                  <h3
                    style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 1.8rem); line-height: 1.2; color: var(--ink); margin: 0;">
                    No ads. No tracking. No subscriptions.
                  </h3>
                </div>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">
                  We know how hard it is to find digital spaces you can trust. That's why we created <strong>The
                    Kidamame Promise</strong>: our apps will never feature advertisements, hidden subscription fees, or
                  confusing in-game currencies. You can <strong>try the app for free</strong> and, if your family loves
                  it, a <strong>single one-time purchase</strong> unlocks the entire world forever. Furthermore,
                  <strong>we collect absolutely no personal data</strong> from your children and the app is <strong>100%
                    offline</strong>. It is a peaceful, secure space where families can play with complete peace of
                  mind.
                </p>
              </div>

              <!-- FAQ SECTION -->
              <div class="faq-section reveal" style="margin-top: 4rem; margin-bottom: 4rem;">
                <h3
                  style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 2rem; text-align: center;">
                  Frequently Asked Questions</h3>

                <div class="faq-list" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem;">
                  <details
                    style="background: white; border: 1.5px solid rgba(58, 158, 228, 0.15); border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem; cursor: pointer;">
                    <summary
                      style="font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); list-style: none; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;">
                      Does Kidamame Discovery have ads?
                      <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down" style="color: var(--blue); font-size: 0.9rem;"></i>
                    </summary>
                    <p style="margin-top: 1rem; color: var(--ink-soft); font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 0;">
                      No. Kidamame Discovery is 100% ad-free. We believe children should be able to explore and learn in
                      a calm environment without interruptions, as advertisements ruin the quality and the flow of the
                      play experience.
                    </p>
                  </details>

                  <details
                    style="background: white; border: 1.5px solid rgba(58, 158, 228, 0.15); border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem; cursor: pointer;">
                    <summary
                      style="font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); list-style: none; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;">
                      Do I need a subscription?
                      <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down" style="color: var(--blue); font-size: 0.9rem;"></i>
                    </summary>
                    <p style="margin-top: 1rem; color: var(--ink-soft); font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 0;">
                      No subscriptions. We offer a simple, transparent pricing model. You can download and try the app
                      for free to see if it's right for your family. If you love it, a single one-time purchase unlocks
                      the entire world of wonder forever.
                    </p>
                  </details>

                  <details
                    style="background: white; border: 1.5px solid rgba(58, 158, 228, 0.15); border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem; cursor: pointer;">
                    <summary
                      style="font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); list-style: none; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;">
                      Is the app completely offline?
                      <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down" style="color: var(--blue); font-size: 0.9rem;"></i>
                    </summary>
                    <p style="margin-top: 1rem; color: var(--ink-soft); font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 0;">
                      Yes! An internet connection is only needed at the time of purchase if you decide to unlock the
                      full app. After that, Kidamame Discovery does not require an internet connection to play. It's
                      truly offline, meaning no tracking, no data collection, and it's perfect for road trips or
                      flights.
                    </p>
                  </details>

                  <details
                    style="background: white; border: 1.5px solid rgba(58, 158, 228, 0.15); border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem; cursor: pointer;">
                    <summary
                      style="font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); list-style: none; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;">
                      How many hours of exploration are there?
                      <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down" style="color: var(--blue); font-size: 0.9rem;"></i>
                    </summary>
                    <p style="margin-top: 1rem; color: var(--ink-soft); font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 0;">
                      Depending on the child's pace, playtime can range from 30 minutes if they just explore and listen
                      to the relaxing sounds, up to 60 minutes or more if they discover and read all the interesting
                      facts with you.
                    </p>
                  </details>

                  <details
                    style="background: white; border: 1.5px solid rgba(58, 158, 228, 0.15); border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem; cursor: pointer;">
                    <summary
                      style="font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); list-style: none; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;">
                      Are there puzzles to solve or levels to unlock?
                      <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down" style="color: var(--blue); font-size: 0.9rem;"></i>
                    </summary>
                    <p style="margin-top: 1rem; color: var(--ink-soft); font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 0;">
                      No. Kidamame is pure exploration and discovery in a Montessori style. It is designed to inspire
                      curiosity about our world and nature without any stressful goals, timers, or scoreboards.
                    </p>
                  </details>

                  <details
                    style="background: white; border: 1.5px solid rgba(58, 158, 228, 0.15); border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem; cursor: pointer;">
                    <summary
                      style="font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); list-style: none; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;">
                      Do you plan to add more biomes or scenes?
                      <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down" style="color: var(--blue); font-size: 0.9rem;"></i>
                    </summary>
                    <p style="margin-top: 1rem; color: var(--ink-soft); font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 0;">
                      We might add one or two scenes, but it's not guaranteed. Because our app is completely offline and
                      all content is included in your download, we have strict storage limits to keep the app size
                      manageable. It's possible we will release new biomes as separate "chapters" in new apps. Sign up
                      for our newsletter below to stay updated on future releases!
                    </p>
                  </details>

                  <details
                    style="background: white; border: 1.5px solid rgba(58, 158, 228, 0.15); border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem; cursor: pointer;">
                    <summary
                      style="font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); list-style: none; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;">
                      What is the recommended age for the app?
                      <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down" style="color: var(--blue); font-size: 0.9rem;"></i>
                    </summary>
                    <p style="margin-top: 1rem; color: var(--ink-soft); font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 0;">
                      Kidamame Discovery is designed for kids ages 4
                      and up, but it grows with them! Younger kids can explore with a parent who can read the facts to
                      them, while older children can delve into the details on their own. Actually, thanks to the
                      fascinating nature facts and the calm, relaxing atmosphere, the app is genuinely engaging for
                      adults too!
                    </p>
                  </details>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- FAQ JSON-LD -->
              <script type="application/ld+json">
              {
                "@context": "https://schema.org",
                "@type": "FAQPage",
                "mainEntity": [{
                  "@type": "Question",
                  "name": "Does Kidamame Discovery have ads?",
                  "acceptedAnswer": {
                    "@type": "Answer",
                    "text": "No. Kidamame Discovery is 100% ad-free. We believe children should be able to explore and learn in a calm environment without interruptions, as advertisements ruin the quality and the flow of the play experience."
                  }
                },{
                  "@type": "Question",
                  "name": "Do I need a subscription?",
                  "acceptedAnswer": {
