                    "text": "Yes! An internet connection is only needed at the time of purchase if you decide to unlock the full app. After that, Kidamame Discovery does not require an internet connection to play. It's truly offline, meaning no tracking, no data collection, and it's perfect for road trips or flights."
                  }
                },{
                  "@type": "Question",
                  "name": "How many hours of exploration are there?",
                  "acceptedAnswer": {
                    "@type": "Answer",
                    "text": "Depending on the child's pace, playtime can range from 30 minutes if they just explore and listen to the relaxing sounds, up to 60 minutes or more if they discover and read all the interesting facts with you."
                  }
                },{
                  "@type": "Question",
                  "name": "Are there puzzles to solve or levels to unlock?",
                  "acceptedAnswer": {
                    "@type": "Answer",
                    "text": "No. Kidamame is pure exploration and discovery in a Montessori style. It is designed to inspire curiosity about our world and nature without any stressful goals, timers, or scoreboards."
                  }
                },{
                  "@type": "Question",
                  "name": "Do you plan to add more biomes or scenes?",
                  "acceptedAnswer": {
                    "@type": "Answer",
                    "text": "We might add one or two scenes, but it's not guaranteed. Because our app is completely offline and all content is included in your download, we have strict storage limits to keep the app size manageable. It's possible we will release new biomes as separate \"chapters\" in new apps. Sign up for our newsletter below to stay updated on future releases!"
                  }
                },{
                  "@type": "Question",
                  "name": "What is the recommended age for the app?",
                  "acceptedAnswer": {
                    "@type": "Answer",
                    "text": "Kidamame Discovery is designed for kids ages 4 and up, but it grows with them! Younger kids can explore with a parent who can read the facts to them, while older children can delve into the details on their own. Actually, thanks to the fascinating nature facts and the calm, relaxing atmosphere, the app is genuinely engaging for adults too!"
                  }
                }]
              }
              </script>

              <div class="reveal"
                style="text-align: center; margin-top: 3.5rem; background: var(--blue-light); padding: 2.5rem 2rem; border-radius: 20px;">
                <h4
                  style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--blue); margin-bottom: 0.8rem;">
                  Stay in the loop!
                </h4>
                <p
                  style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--ink-soft); max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 1.5rem; line-height: 1.6;">
                  Want to be the first to know when <strong>Kidamame Discovery</strong> launches on the Google Play
                  Store and the Apple App Store? Sign
                  up
                  to our newsletter for updates, behind-the-scenes content, and early access opportunities!
                </p>
                <a href="https://kidamame.substack.com/subscribe" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
                  class="btn-primary">
                  ✨ Join our newsletter
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
      </main>

      <%- include('../partials/new-footer') %>
  </body>

</html>